text_fr: En couple, votre vie sentimentale n'a rien d'un long fleuve tranquille, il faudra s'attendre à rencontrer des tensions. Célibataire, même quand la séduction semble jouer à cache-chache, ne baissez pas les bras.
text_en: On a sentimental level, poorly aspected Venus puts obstacles in your way.

text_en: Today is the time to examine the fine print of contracts to avoid any unpleasant surprises: thoroughness always pays.

text_en: You manage to concentrate your patience and your efforts to achieve your goals, your sporting practice will benefit. text_en: The simple pleasures in life give you the most joy: you enjoy a chat over a meal. Your sarcasm isn't to everyone's taste, but you don't care. You could live an original experience with friends.

text_fr: À deux, vous avez droit à des jours de douceur bien mérités côté coeur, profitez-en ! Même si vous avez tendance à fuir le quotidien, il peut aussi apporter sa part de moments précieux. Quant aux célibataires, vous semblez particulièrement encline à de nouvelles rencontres.
text_en: On a sentimental level, poorly aspected Venus puts obstacles in your way. Single, know that haste will not pay off, it may even harm you if you make decisions too quickly. As a couple, the curiosity and authenticity you demonstrate will be appreciated by your other half.

text_en: Paris, compulsive purchases and consumerist temptations are your nemesis: keep your head on your shoulders and watch your personal finances, the time has come for rationality.

text_fr: Une sieste vous aidera à faire le plein de force en cas de fatigue, mais vous vous sentez en forme. Dans une forme olympique, vous devriez jouir de cet élan positif, qui pourrait vous valoir de belles surprises.
text_en: The day is looking particularly good, luck seems to be smiling on you and everything is simpler! In Olympic form, you should enjoy this positive momentum, which could earn you some nice surprises. You shake up your habits, but try to maintain a semblance of routine.

text_fr: Au travail, vous êtes productive et organisée, et cela ne passe pas inaperçu.
text_en: Someone in your professional circle could tell you a secret, you could help improve the atmosphere at work. You take your imagination very seriously and you could bring artistic inspirations to life.

text_fr: Vous avez tendance à contester l'autorité, et si cela pourrait s'avérer positif en cas d'injustices, ne vous enfermez pas dans une posture de désobéissance obtuse.
text_en: You are structured and manage to organize your home well, now is a good time to plan this family meal that everyone is looking forward to.
